(3619, 1, '2020-03-11 04:41:10', '2020-03-10 21:41:10', 'Evaluate suppliers’ capabilities and responsible business practices based on international standards.		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit.jpg 750w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		<p>Ensure proven quality and compliance of your purchased equipment of industrial facilities, successful and effective production. Equipment has to meet quoted or contractually guaranteed specifications prior to delivery and final installation. Our factory acceptance testing services provide verification that all technical and quality requirements have been met before a component leaves the factory.</p><p>As an independent verification and certification company, we support your project or manufacturing process with extensive services along the supply chain. We ensure design specifications and prove the quality of your ordered equipment and components.</p><p> </p>Our factory audit service firstly helps you to identify the potential risk at the earliest stage. Our experienced auditors performs on-site check at factory to ensure good working conditions in which no underlying harm to the staff and no illegal employee violate the law by evaluating the code of conduct, management system, production facilities, production control, production capability and scheduling, quality control and more.\nOur factory acceptance testing services offer extensive solutions to ensure the quality and compliance with specifications and contractual requirements for equipment and components. Make sure that your equipment or plant performs as expected under a full range of foreseeable conditions and avoid costly contractual penalties if you are a manufacturer or project downtimes if you are an operator.\n<p>Contact us to ensure proven quality of your purchase and request a quote.</p>', 'Factory Check', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'factory-check', '', '', '2020-03-11 04:51:12', '2020-03-10 21:51:12', '', 3615, 'https://indogoods.id/?page_id=3619', 0, 'page', '', 0),
