(3630, 1, '2020-03-11 05:07:36', '2020-03-10 22:07:36', '<img width=\"1398\" height=\"1904\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/purchase-order.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/purchase-order.jpg 1398w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/purchase-order-220x300.jpg 220w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/purchase-order-768x1046.jpg 768w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/purchase-order-752x1024.jpg 752w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1398px) 100vw, 1398px\" />											\n		<p><strong>INDO GOODS</strong> is an international trading company.<br />Located in Semarang (Indonesia), Dubai (UAE) and Beirut (Lebanon) we are a specialized procurement services company dedicated to helping our clients improve their bottom line.</p>		\n		<style type=\'text/css\'>\n			#gallery-1 {\n				margin: auto;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 .gallery-item {\n				float: left;\n				margin-top: 10px;\n				text-align: center;\n				width: 33%;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 img {\n				border: 2px solid #cfcfcf;\n			}\n			#gallery-1 .gallery-caption {\n				margin-left: 0;\n			}\n			/* see gallery_shortcode() in wp-includes/media.php */\n		</style>\n		<dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a data-madxartwork-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-madxartwork-lightbox-slideshow=\"0abf79a\" href=\'https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_162848_657.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"212\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_162848_657-300x212.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_162848_657-300x212.jpg 300w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_162848_657-768x542.jpg 768w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_162848_657.jpg 905w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a data-madxartwork-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-madxartwork-lightbox-slideshow=\"0abf79a\" href=\'https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079-300x300.jpg 300w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079-150x150.jpg 150w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079-768x768.jpg 768w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_164232_079.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><dl class=\'gallery-item\'>\n			<dt class=\'gallery-icon landscape\'>\n				<a data-madxartwork-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-madxartwork-lightbox-slideshow=\"0abf79a\" href=\'https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728.jpg\'><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728-300x300.jpg 300w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728-150x150.jpg 150w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728-768x768.jpg 768w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_20200319_165248_728.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>\n			</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" />\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit.jpg 750w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/supplier-audit-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/shipping-check.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/shipping-check.jpg 750w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/shipping-check-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		<p>We believe in quality control inspections, factory audit and supplier evaluations, and consumer product testing are constantly being improved to ensure we provide the best in class services to you. Our passion to consistently deliver the highest in standards of service is what defines.</p>		\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/quality-control-necessary-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/quality-control-necessary-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/quality-control-necessary-300x169.jpg 300w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/quality-control-necessary-768x432.jpg 768w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/quality-control-necessary.jpg 1400w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n		<p>Indo Goods trading company capable of adding value and finding appropriate factories to make your goods.Knowing what traits to look for in a prospective supplier can help you avoid mistakenly committing to one that isn’t suitable. And that can only mean good things for you, your customers and your bottom line.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Mission</strong><br />Our mission is to operate the best general trades business in the world, and we would like to Introducing Indonesia product to the market and to be the most competitive and trusted quality control provider in the world. Above all, we expect to surpass our clients expectations and add value to the communities we serve.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Vision</strong><br />Our vision is to be one of the business bench marks in general trades and revolutionize this company to have all the strengths of a large company combined with the leanness and agility of a medium company. We want “ Indo Goods “ Trading Company to be known as the premier trade partner that fosters a work environment that encourages new ideas, new innovations and sustainable growth. We will continuous improvement driven by our core values.</p>', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2020-03-22 09:26:10', '2020-03-22 02:26:10', '', 0, 'https://indogoods.id/?page_id=3630', 1, 'page', '', 0),
