(3638, 1, '2020-03-11 05:24:34', '2020-03-10 22:24:34', '<p>Experience with local courts and regulations to arrange a legal courier for your next shipment</p>		\n										<img width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/legal-document-check.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/legal-document-check.jpg 750w, https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/legal-document-check-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" />											\n		Our services provide you export and import document proceeding services, export and import custom clearance, and ship chartering with its crew.We manage all the documentation related to the shipment and any form of merchandise purchases/sales: letter of credits, shipment verified by document hand-over, contracts, etc. We track all of this digitally, allowing us to manage and verify all processes in a more productive and effective way.', 'Legal Document', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'legal-document', '', '', '2020-03-11 05:33:53', '2020-03-10 22:33:53', '', 3615, 'https://indogoods.id/?page_id=3638', 0, 'page', '', 0),
