(3654, 1, '2020-03-15 05:23:55', '2020-03-14 22:23:55', 'Indonesia is one of the top coffee producing countries in the world, and is home to several islands that are renowned for their coffee. Earthy flavors are somewhat of an acquired taste, and it is for that reason that Indonesian coffees are often held in the highest of regard by more experienced coffee drinkers.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3645\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/coffe-bean-7-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\nIn general these coffees are known for their full-bodied, rich taste and vibrant yet low-toned and gentle acidity, and long finish / aftertaste. Some Indonesian coffees are quite earthy in flavour, a quality loved by some people but overpowering to others and take some getting used to, to be fully appreciated.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3646\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/coffe-bean-8-300x104.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"104\" />\r\nMost coffees from Indonesia are highly prized for their complex, spice-y flavors thanks to the rich soils and idyllic growing conditions. Among the best reviewed Indonesian coffees, Sumatra and Sulawesi frequently take the top spots - this is in part due to the more prevalent processing and exporting industries and strong government support. We recommend trying coffees from all the regions however, as they\'re all a treat to enjoy.', 'Coffee Bean', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'coffee-bean', '', '', '2020-03-15 05:23:55', '2020-03-14 22:23:55', '', 0, 'https://indogoods.id/?p=3654', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(3658, 1, '2020-03-15 06:09:52', '2020-03-14 23:09:52', 'Indonesia Virgin Coconut Oil are cooperate with many coconut farmers from Sumatra, Sulawesi, and Java to provide top quality coconut oil and related products. With the ever increasing demand of virgin coconut oil both internally and internationally Indonesia continually strive to grow and build establishing factory throughout Indonesia\r\n\r\nExperiences in the edible oil industry provide deep understanding on the global marketplace as well as in the community and its demands. We deliver to the global market, work with qualified suppliers from all around the world, and abreast with the latest technological development factory. Without putting aside the importance of environment and our surroundings, adopt a safe and environmentally friendly manufacturing practices to create the best products.', 'Coconut Oil', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'coconut-oil', '', '', '2020-03-15 06:09:52', '2020-03-14 23:09:52', '', 0, 'https://indogoods.id/?p=3658', 0, 'post', '', 0),
