(3660, 1, '2020-03-15 06:18:59', '2020-03-14 23:18:59', 'Indonesian furniture industry has shown its competitiveness in a global market with its unique and competitive products. Indonesia has long been known as one of the world\'s leading furniture manufacturers. Its teak and rattan products are sought after in both the local and international markets.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3647\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/furniture-1-300x96.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"96\" />\r\n\r\nThe traditional markets for Indonesia\'s furniture products are the United States, Europe, and China. In recent years, the furniture industry has begun to tap into non-traditional markets too such as Africa, the Middle East, and Eastern Europe.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-3649\" src=\"https://indogoods.id/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/furniture-3-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" />\r\n\r\nWe helping you to have the existing furniture you want. By working with the best furniture manufactures in Indonesia, we ensure you have a good service in determining your furniture choices.', 'Furniture', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'furniture', '', '', '2020-03-15 06:18:59', '2020-03-14 23:18:59', '', 0, 'https://indogoods.id/?p=3660', 0, 'post', '', 0),
